OL,3,CFamilies of UVF shooting victims 'not
OL,4,Cgiving up' after inquiry request
OL,5,Crefused
OL,7,FThe families of four people killed by
OL,8,Floyalists in Co Tyrone in 1992 have
OL,9,Fvowed never to give up after their
OL,10,Frequest for a public inquiry was
OL,11,Frefused.
OL,13,FKevin McKearney, 32, was shot dead by
OL,14,Fa UVF gunman inside his family-run
OL,15,Fbutcher shop in the village of Moy in
OL,16,FJanuary 1992. His uncle Jack
OL,17,FMcKearney, 69, was wounded in the same
OL,18,Fattack and died in hospital three
OL,19,Fmonths later.
