OL,7,FLater that year, Kevin McKearney's
OL,8,Fmother-in-law and father-in-law,
OL,9,FCharlie and Teresa Fox ` who were 63
OL,10,Fand 54 respectively ` were shot dead
OL,11,Fby the UVF inside their home in Moy.
OL,13,FEarlier this year, a coroner said he
OL,14,Fhad been prevented from delivering a
OL,15,F"narrative" around the events
OL,16,Ffollowing a legal challenge from the
OL,17,FGovernment to it being delivered in
OL,18,Fopen court.
