OL,4,Cgiving up' after inquiry request
OL,5,Crefused
OL,7,FJudge Richard Greene KC also said he
OL,8,Fhad reached a provisional view that an
OL,9,Finquest into the four deaths could not
OL,10,Fproceed because of the withholding of
OL,11,Fsensitive files from the proceedings
OL,12,Fon national security grounds.
OL,14,FOn Thursday, the families said
OL,15,FSecretary of State Hilary Benn had
OL,16,Frefused their request for a public
OL,17,Finquiry, instead recommending it be
OL,18,Finvestigated by the Independent
OL,19,FCommission for Reconciliation and
OL,20,FInformation Recovery (ICRIR).
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
