OL,7,FThe McKearney family has vowed they
OL,8,Fwill not give up and will not accept
OL,9,Fan investigation by the body set up by
OL,10,Fthe previous government's Legacy Act.
OL,12,FKevin McKearney's widow Bernie said:
OL,13,F"We as a family are not giving up.
OL,15,F"Our inquest was stopped by the
OL,16,Fcoroner and a public inquiry was
OL,17,Frecommended.
