OL,7,F"We want our inquiry and are not
OL,8,Faccepting a lesser body like the
OL,9,FICRIR. Unfortunately, this Secretary
OL,10,Fof State is no different than those
OL,11,Fbefore him and now we will proceed to
OL,12,Fcourt to challenge him."
OL,14,FKevin McKearney's sister Angela
OL,15,FMcKearney added: "We will continue our
OL,16,Fcampaign for justice and now move for
OL,17,Fan urgent judicial review against the
OL,18,Fdecision of the Secretary of State."
