OL,7,FSolicitor Gavin Booth of Phoenix Law
OL,8,Fchallenged the Labour Government for
OL,9,Fnot having repealed or replaced the
OL,10,FLegacy Act.
OL,12,F"It has not repealed any of the Act,
OL,13,Fstill less replaced it. Instead, in
OL,14,Fthis decision, the Secretary of State
OL,15,Fhas expressed its 'full confidence' in
OL,16,Fa body which is not independent, and
OL,17,Fwhich was expressly designed to
OL,18,Fprotect state officers and agents from
OL,19,Fbeing held to account," he said.
OL,21,F"This decision is a disgrace.
