OL,7,F"To be clear, the families do not
OL,8,Faccept that the ICRIR is capable of
OL,9,Fdischarging the state's obligation to
OL,10,Ftheir family.
OL,12,F"The family has no faith in this body
OL,13,Fand no amount of window dressing will
OL,14,Fchange this family's view and the view
OL,15,Fof all legacy families of the ICRIR.
OL,17,F"The Secretary of State should now
OL,18,Fabolish the ICRIR."
