OL,7,F"He expressed his enormous sympathy
OL,8,Ffor the families, and encouraged them
OL,9,Fto meet with Sir Declan Morgan to hear
OL,10,Fhow the Independent Commission on
OL,11,FReconciliation and Information
OL,12,FRecovery would approach an
OL,13,Finvestigation into the deaths of their
OL,14,Floved ones."
