OL,7,F29-year-old Fergal McCusker from
OL,8,FMaghera was killed at the back of a
OL,9,Fyouth club on January 18 1998.
OL,11,FThe loyalist group the LVF at the time
OL,12,Fclaimed responsibility for the killing.
OL,14,FNo one has ever been prosecuted or
OL,15,Fconvicted over his death.
