OL,7,FThe families' legal representative,
OL,8,FPadraig O Muirigh, said: "This
OL,9,Fdecision by the British Secretary of
OL,10,FState to refuse a public inquiry into
OL,11,FFergal's death is a further sad and
OL,12,Ffrustrating development for the
OL,13,FMcCusker family who have fought
OL,14,Ftirelessly for a proper investigation
OL,15,Ffor the 26 years since his death."
